# Dependencies & build outputs
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.vite
client/dist
server/public

# Env / secrets — pass at runtime (-e / --env-file), never bake into the image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Git / IDE / OS
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.cursor
.vscode
.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.swp
**/*~

# Logs & coverage
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# Local runtime data (mount a volume if needed)
saved
**/saved

# Docs / misc that are not needed to build or run
**/*.md
!README.md
agent-transcripts
**/agent-tools
# Cursor scratch media (do NOT ignore server/assets/model-images)
.cursor/**/assets

# Nested locks inside dependencies (safety)
**/node_modules/**/package-lock.json
